Company Description: Founded IN 1955, Mcdonald S Is A Global Food Service Retailer That Operates More Than 30,000 Locations IN Over 100 Countries. The Restaurant Serves Various Shakes, Hamburgers, Grilled And Fried Chicken Products, Salads, Fruits, Sandwiches And Fish. It Additionally Offers French Fries, Chicken Sandwiches, Quarter Pounders And Honey Wheat Rolls. The Restaurant S Menu Also Includes The Ranch Snack Wrap, Big N' Tasty, Chicken Selects And Mcflurry Treats. It Serves A Variety Of Beverages And Desserts, Including Chocolate Triple Thick, Minty Mudd Bath Triple Thick And Strawberry Triple Thick Shakes And Mcdonaldland Cookies. The Restaurant Serves Nearly 50 Million People Each Day. Mcdonald S Restaurants Are Owned And Operated By Independent Franchisees Of Mcdonald's Corporation.

Established IN 1948, Mcdonald's Corporation Is A Fast Food Company. Based IN Barnegat, N.J., It Is A Global Foodservice Retailer Operating One Of The Largest Chains Of Franchised Outlets. Its Menu Consists Of Various Items, Including Burgers, Sandwiches, Salads, Beverages And Desserts. Some Of Its Flagship Products Include Big Mac Sandwich, Quarter Pounder, Chicken Mcnuggets, Egg Mcmuffin And Mcgourmet Dinners. Mcdonald's Provides Both Fruit And Vegetable Option For Its Happy Meals, Such As Fruit Bags, Corn Cups And Apple Dippers. The Company Also Offers Entertainment Options Such As Free WI-Fi, Arch Card/Play Places And Party Services. For Over 20 Years, Mcdonald's Partners The Environmental Defense Fund.
